{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_13_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 ど、努力します",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこれは私からの気持ちです、受け取って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4448.072465299999,
          "startTime": 6.7814057986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　これ、俺がもらっていいのか？\n琴乃からのプレゼントなんて、なんだろうなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4814057986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "チョコレートです\n{user}さんの口に合えばいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　でも、か、勘違いしないで下さいね\nこれはあくまで、いつもお世話になってるお礼ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、義理チョコでも、もらえるだけで嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6766667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁこの前は、芽衣が「本命だよ」なんて言って\n渡してくるから、あれはちょっと焦ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4433334033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ほ、本命チョコを！？\n芽衣が、{user}さんに！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いやいや、誤解なんだ。本人はどうも\n『本命』の意味がよく分かってなかったみたいでな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8536500295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ああ、そういうことですか\n芽衣ってば、なんでそんな変な覚え方しちゃったんだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……それにしても、本命かぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8770995458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか思い出し笑いをしてますけど\n他にも、本命がどうとか言ってた人がいたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ\n昔、麻奈がバレンタインのCMに出たことがあってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.43476305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そのCMなら私も見ました\nお姉ちゃん、凄く楽しそうに演じてましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "撮影の前、麻奈は「本命は琴乃だよ」なんて言っててな\nそのことを今、ふと思い出したんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5968036651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃんが？\nいえ、嬉しくない訳じゃないんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんってば、そんなことばっか言ってるから\n最後まで{user}さんと……まったくもう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、麻奈と言えば……って訳でもないんだが\n例の曲の件、進捗はどんな感じだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1389352481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "え……ええと……\nそのことでちょっと、相談したいことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でもチョコレートはあくまで日頃のお礼ですから\nこのための賄賂とか、そんなんじゃないですからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.7228574436
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.7228574436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（しばらく前から琴乃は『song for you』と）\n（対になる麻奈へのアンサーソング作りに取り組んでいる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9884469669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（だが、お披露目予定のソロライブツアーが）\n（迫りつつある今もまだ、曲は完成していない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3395241102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.3728574436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "本当にすみません！\n曲作りのために、あと少しだけ時間をもらえませんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.0366212528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "自分から新曲をやりたいって言ったくせに\n作業が遅くて、迷惑掛けてるのは分かってるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お姉ちゃんの曲への返事ですから\n中途半端なところで、妥協したくはなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 173.7472117108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。こんな時のためにマネージャーがいるんだ\n調整は俺がやるから、琴乃は曲作りに専念してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.4805450441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 181.7138783774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、ありがとうございます！\nでも、その……怒ってはいませんか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、慣れてるからな。前にも似たような……\nいや、もっと大変だったこともあったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7371007922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 198.3704341255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "前にも？　こんな日程がずれ込んだことありましたっけ\n……あ、もしかして……お姉ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ\n麻奈が『song for you』を作った時にな",
      "translations": {
